<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/coronavirus-is-a-historic-trigger-event-we-need-a-massive-movement-in-response/" title="Coronavirus Is a Historic Trigger Event. We Need a Massive Movement in Response.">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1214142596-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="People walk by a closed storefront" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1214142596-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1214142596-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1214142596-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1214142596-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1214142596-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
