<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/coronavirus-is-a-historic-trigger-event-we-need-a-massive-movement-in-response/">Coronavirus Is a Historic Trigger Event. We Need a Massive Movement in Response.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Even in times of social distancing, building a collective, social response to the pandemic is our only salvation.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/paul-engler/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Paul Engler</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://wagingnonviolence.org/2020/03/coronavirus-historic-trigger-event-needs-movement-response/?fbclid=IwAR1rhPhvojOi4sbBhC0hTDRrA_QuqCJFA7oczXorG7SLRDBYPpWKwPtW0jo' itemprop='url'>Waging Nonviolence</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2020-03-23T16:24:14+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2020-03-23T16:24:14+00:00">March 23, 2020</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
</a>
</div>
